reviews.text: Perfect Sirolin Steak! Love it. Cozy restaurant with reasonable price. And the staff are friendly too!
Great pizza and friendly staff. Nice table outside if you want to eat al fresco.
A Mui Wo staple good food reasonable price. The rack of ribs is great

Not a kids friendly place. The asian server ignored us deliberately. We were a big group consisted of kids and elderlies. The guy walked away intentionally from our table when we tried to order. His face was so pissed off, because we were speaking in Cantonese? The restaurant was not busy at that time. And I don't understand why the server said namaste to us at an Italian restaurant...
